1 year ago today I got to retire from being a Stripper!
Remember putting my makeup on and being in a fight camp. I was so tired I just didn’t know how I was going to stay awake let alone have the energy to do gymnastics all night, be cheerful, and entertaining. All I dreamed about was getting to follow my dreams and fight full time. 

I believed I was good enough! Walked away that night and never look back. It was one of the scariest things I’d done. Didn’t have the means to do it, I was going to make it happen!!! That next fight was the beginning of the best year of my life. 

The scariest thing I ever did, jump started the life I always dreamed of…. We’re just getting started🫶🧡🥳

There’s no freaking way I could have done this alone!!! There’s so many people that stand by me that loved me as I was, encouraged me and believed in me. Thank you guys. It may have been my decision, there’s no way I can do it without you!!!
The Avatar came out lookin like a freakin BadAss!! This life chose me😝

LEVELS🏆🔥 
Honored to be in a room like this one.

🥋Jiujitsu is hard to understand without experiencing it🥋
🔥Send this to someone you want to understand learning Jiujitsu🔥
The way I’ve always introduced people is by explaining a giant puzzle. You know what the picture is suppose to look like but you don’t have any pieces to put it together. Every time you go to class you get to earn a piece of the puzzle. Bringing you closer to the overall vision. 
When you’re new it’s hard to see any progress, until a new person comes to class and you get to share with them. 
Jiujitsu is a fascinating sport. Constantly growing and evolving. Mental and Physical. There’s always danger, at the same time you always have an opportunity to TAP and try again. 
Fall in love with learning. 
Fall in love with growing.
Fall in love with learning some BadAss Shit🔥

Thanx @abcnation115 for catching this🤭 Had no idea you were filming. 📸

ONE YEAR AGO🏆
This was such an awesome moment! Thanx @joerogan for enjoying that with me. The magnitude is that getting interviewed means WINNING a fight in the UFC🔥😍
Can’t even explain how amazing this moment is. I get to go out and continue living my dreams with @ufc🥊 
Time to buckle up the seatbelt. It’s a wild ride and we just began!!

comp training with my girl 💚
@lilmonsterdemo

There’s two ways to get after it in life…

You work yourself toward the goal  little by little, or…
You dive head first in and FITFO.

When @lilmonsterdemo comes into town head first made the most sense so we dove in and did the incline to get her acclimated to CO.

We had one set of rules: don’t stop and take it one step at a time with a child like mentality. Little by little we climbed.

It was a great trip.

Saturday is the separator and today that blocked was checked.

I hope you got after it on Suffering Saturday too.

🗡

Gave up a seemingly glamorous lifestyle for one of Glory. 
Traded my high heels for gloves.
The long nights for long days.
The hair and make up for blood and sweat.
The lingerie for workout shorts.

The money was costing me. It was robbing me of who I’m meant to be. A Champion.

Took a chance on myself. Invested in me. Choose to chase my dreams instead of chasing dollars.

It was the scariest and most liberating thing I had ever done. God continues to gift me and show me how following His journey for my life is always the right way. 

Do what you gotta do until you can do what you wanna do. Stay true to yourself. Don’t be robbed of life by things that aren’t truly valuable. Love yourself enough to get what the fuck you deserve. Create a world worth living in.

I am the STAR of my own show!! ✨
Yes I stood on my booth and started dancing for the hundreds of people standing in line to meet us fighters🫶
Grateful to be able to share so much love with all of you. 
I have always been wild and crazy!! I love to yell and dance and live life at a million miles an hour. If you got to meet me this weekend I tried to slow everything down and spend quality time with all of you. You matter!! You matter to me. Thank you for letting me be all of me, and excepting me exactly as I come.

The rebuild. Mathew 16:18
The part no one wants to endure. The building process. I’m grateful for the chapters that make me stretch further and fight harder.

My journey is filled with public ups and downs. You’ve seen me rise, you’ve seen me fall short, you’ve NEVER seen me quit! Life takes me to a lot of places, blessed for the opportunities. Excited to be living parts of the story I’ve always known were possible. Even more excited to create the parts no one thinks can come true. 

I am a Warrior! I am Powerful! I will Thrive!

He’s someone I trust whole heartedly. Thank you Professor for always believing in me🔥🔥 Even when things weren’t always so bright ✨

My Pappou was my #1 ❤️🫶❤️ 
It’s been a week since he left us. I loved him with all my heart! Was raised by my grandparents so he was my father figure. Truly when I look back on my time with him I know without a doubt how much we loved each other🥹 
I was always pestering and love bombing him endearingly. Couldn’t believe it when he learned how to use FaceTime and would call consistently 🥰 
He was more than proud of me. I have confidence and comfort for the memories we have and the time spent together. 
Take all the videos!! Take all the pictures!! Be annoying with how much love you give to the people that matter the most😘 
Love you all. Thank you to everyone for the support. 

Dear Pappou, 
Promise to keep making you proud. Thank you for supporting me even though you always thought I was a little crazy sometimes. Love you with absolutely my whole entire heart. I’ll keep spreading my wings to fly and live my life. Happy you got to fully live yours. I miss you so so much. Your memory will always be with me Pappou❤️❤️❤️
